      <lg type="edition">
<l>vicumpiḻi tōkaic cīrpōṉ ṟiciṉē</l>
<l>pacumpo ṉaviriḻai paiya niḻaṟṟak</l>
<l>karaicēr maruta mēṟip</l>
<l>paṇṇai pāyvō ṭaṇṇaṟuṅ katuppē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

  
<l>   Climbing into the Myrobalan tree by the shore,</l> 
<l rend="indent2"> 	so that [her] jewels shining with green gold sparkled softly, </l> 
<l rend="indent4"> 				she would jump into the tank. </l> 
<l> May her cool, fragrant locks [as she jumps] </l> 
<l> resemble the grace of a peacock feather floating down from the sky! </l> 


  
  
  </lg>
